When he does not even have news of Jeremy , Dylan will come to his aid .

Die Zwölf - Zurück in die Gegenwart

description: After the horrific fruition of Harold and Nadine's plans last issue, everything in the Free Zone hangs in the balance. Newly returned from the wilderness, Mother Abagail clings to life, just barely, prompting city-wide fear and unrest. Meanwhile, the surviving members of the Committee keep vigil by her bedside, unprepared for her latest revelation: That the time has come for the forces of good to make a stand against Flagg's armies of darkness in the west... The stage is set, True Believers, the die is cast, and it's time to choose sides, as this shattering arc concludes!

name: Moon Knight - Der Tod von Marc Spector

description: Seven souls find themselves, because of a mysterious invitation, at the dark castle of Xanador . So Dylan , Lucinda , Benjamin , Julian , Clumsy , Scrooge and Mary are trapped with no way out in the castle , where sinister puppets walk around, manipulated by a mysterious host . Benjamin is the first to die , and the survivors try to escape, but  the fate wants them to return to Xanador . No one knows that death itself is one of the seven .
name: Sette anime dannate

Lord Wells calls Dylan and four other " variously sensitive " people and subjects them to an experiment : for five days they will sleep and dream together in order to find out if they can dream the same dream. During the experiment they will explore anguish , buried memories , complexes , to finally find themselves.
The story contains hints and anticipationsabout the then upcoming Dylan Dog #100.
